													<p>I got about halfway through before I gave up reading the rest.  This is a rediculous idea.  It can be gamed as badly as the Democratic proportional system.   By running up huge vote totals in highly polarized states, you could completely game this system.</p>
<p>Sorry, I don't buy into this idea of small states deserving a bigger say.</p>
<p>1 person - 1 vote.</p>
<p>Nothing more, nothing less.  If you can't do that, then keep it as it is.</p>
